data.description: A MUST SEE unit! Upgraded with stone counters, High back splash, tile floors & beautiful cabinets in a highly DESIRABLE property in a cul-de-sac.  Rarely Available TWO bedroom TWO Bath unit in Salt lake with a washer & Dryer inside your unit. And then there is the great amenities:  Pool, Rec room, grounds, Security, On-site Manager & Guest parking...  To TOP it all off…. It is in town. Have you heard everyone say it’s all about Location, Location, Location… Well, this property is in Honolulu near Tripler Army Medical Center, Kaiser Hospital facilities, Golfing, Shopping, Dining, Elementary, Middle and High Schools.  Maintenance Fee includes Central AC, Electricity, water/sewer, basic Cable & Wifi. A 1st Open Sun. Jan. 28, 2 to 5 pm
